NIST control group
===============


AC: Access Control — 24 controls

AT: Awareness and Training — 6 controls

AU: Audit and Accountability — 14 controls

CA: Assessment, Authorization, and Monitoring — 9 controls

CM: Configuration Management — 14 controls

CP: Contingency Planning — 10 controls

IA: Identification and Authentication — 13 controls

IR: Incident Response — 9 controls

MA: Maintenance — 6 controls

MP: Media Protection — 10 controls

PE: Physical and Environmental Protection — 20 controls

PL: Planning — 7 controls

PS: Personnel Security — 8 controls

PT: PII Processing and Transparency — 6 controls

RA: Risk Assessment — 8 controls

SA: System and Services Acquisition — 15 controls

SC: System and Communications Protection — 45 controls

SI: System and Information Integrity — 19 controls

SR: Supply Chain Risk Management — 12 controls


